    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes extensions to "Bit Index Explicit Replication Traffic Engineering" (BIER-TE) for supporting LANs (i.e., broadcast links). For a multicast packet with an explicit point-to-multipoint (P2MP) path traversing LANs, the packet is replicated and forwarded statelessly along the path.</t>
